{"tid":362443,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"林志穎被追問「拿到iPhone 8未？」　機神露玄機：聽說HOME鍵取消","createTime":"2017-08-17T02:29:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T15:18:20.000Z","uid":105243,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a8ace0f7a67716a877f7cce0ba8a0e0e4b2edc9","tid":362443,"uid":105243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T02:29:29.000Z","msg":"林志穎被追問「拿到iPhone 8未？」　<strong>機神露玄機：聽說HOME鍵取消</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/112416/thumbnail/3f7666007b3f01d831ce96a10b6288bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F112416%2Fthumbnail%2F3f7666007b3f01d831ce96a10b6288bd.jpg&h=40815fb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨著iPhone 8的流出的消息越來越多，就代表著新iPhone發佈會越來越接近，網上流傳發佈日期是9月17日，而開售就是在9月25日，有傳今次iPhone將會大革新，除了機身會採用全新設計之外，最重要是經典Home鍵將會由實體鍵改為虛擬鍵，雖則今次傳售價將會過萬，但相信定必掠起一股「抄Phone熱潮」。<br />\n<br />\n消息屬真屬假真的要等發佈那天才知道，網上流言那麼多，網民卻只相信「不老男神」林志穎，皆因每次蘋果發佈新機之前，他總會搶先拿到新機在微博上「不經意」上曝光，由7年前的iPad mini到上年的iPhone 7 Plus，他所展示的蘋果產品與與真正發佈的幾乎是一模一樣，被網民供奉做「iPhone大神」，大家都懷疑他是不是「走後門」，與蘋果的人有關係，但蘋果方面曾表示：「肯定不是真的，公司沒有發表新機，一切網路傳言，都與公司無關。」但網民依舊表示：「我只相信林志穎。」<br />\n<br />\n今日林志穎出席腕錶展時被問到他拿到新iPhone 8沒有，他沒有正面回答：「聽說HOME鍵有取消，很想知道怎麼回到主畫面，目前也是跟大家在網上的資訊一樣。」，難道大神已經拿到最新的iPhone 8，照他這個說法，HOME鍵是肯定取消了，當被大家一再追問新機事宜，他笑言：「我不知道，我不是代言人，未來也不會再說什麼。」既然他封口不說，網民們只好去蹲林志穎的微博，看看什麼時候他再曝光蘋果新機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/娛樂/112416/林志穎被追問-拿到iPhone-8未-機神露玄機-聽說HOME鍵取消\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2F112416%2F%E6%9E%97%E5%BF%97%E7%A9%8E%E8%A2%AB%E8%BF%BD%E5%95%8F-%E6%8B%BF%E5%88%B0iPhone-8%E6%9C%AA-%E6%A9%9F%E7%A5%9E%E9%9C%B2%E7%8E%84%E6%A9%9F-%E8%81%BD%E8%AA%AAHOME%E9%8D%B5%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88&d=UlEy9l6EmTdir9krYDVFQZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=170059b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/娛樂/112416/林志穎被追問-拿到iPhone-8未-機神露玄機-聽說HOME鍵取消</a>"},{"pid":"ba31fa4b9fbdff092e5a01c6e5a6f652e90191e8","tid":362443,"uid":125333,"like":54,"dislike":5,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:23:12.000Z","msg":"年年拎部dummy機抄高自己人氣 收皮啦"},{"pid":"c0c22537258aecd78585b1bc2a9fb4a68081afd7","tid":362443,"uid":4917,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:27:29.000Z","msg":"呢條拉皮怪識富士康廠D人咋嘛<br />\n支那人要威要面，一有新嘢忍唔住就要曬"},{"pid":"f857642f99003315ba5398f24b1690db2f12c9cf","tid":362443,"uid":137625,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:34:03.000Z","msg":"咁撚威唔撚影埋自己條撚放上網"},{"pid":"117e3178e537e79c70ecf7e0d8d6da0c91f491d7","tid":362443,"uid":101201,"like":5,"dislike":35,"score":-30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:37:22.000Z","msg":"連登仔連林志穎都反？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a03113874fe9071ac2ae15aec56fc7d5fcbffdb9","tid":362443,"uid":137625,"like":82,"dislike":10,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:41:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登仔連林志穎都反？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊撚個林志穎咁撚大枝野呀？屌柒佢唔撚得呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48126dd565a922cfe7d09b9b4ffd76e314ee215","tid":362443,"uid":281,"like":21,"dislike":15,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:00:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f58d037ad5d0e562edfc72d5acd13b509862876","tid":362443,"uid":25002,"like":7,"dislike":12,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:01:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4808e5e7ead9ae87510ee70edefb3f51fa7adc9d","tid":362443,"uid":3063,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:06:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連登仔連林志穎都反？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊撚個林志穎咁撚大枝野呀？屌柒佢唔撚得呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />